snippet.title: Sally Face, Episode One: Strange Neighbors (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Sally Face is a boy with a prosthetic face and a mysterious past. In the first episode of his adventure, Sal explores his new apartment building, meets Strange Neighbors and helps solve an unfortunate crime. 

Play Sally Face: http://store.steampowered.com/app/541570

Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PortableMoose
Follow on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/portablemoose/

Thanks for watching!
